# Tanker

FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + Alembic scaffold for single-customer deployments.

## Quick Start

```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -e .
Copy-Item .env.example .env
```

Update `.env` values, then run:

```powershell
alembic upgrade head
tanker-seed-base
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Health check:
- `GET /healthz`
